version 0.1 beta

ChromePhp is a PHP class to go along with the ChromePhp Google Chrome extension.

This class allows you to log variables to the Chrome console.

INSTALLATION
1.  put ChromePhp.php somewhere in your PHP include path
2.  include 'ChromePhp.php';
3.  ChromePhp::log('hello world');

More information can be found here:
http://www.craigiam.com/chromephp
